# Copy to .env.local for local dev, or set these in Vercel → Project → Settings →
# Environment Variables. With NO key set, the bundled-sample demo still works
# (boxes + JSON come from baked ground truth); a key enables live extraction on
# documents you upload.

# Required for live extraction on uploaded documents:
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
